e="preserve">Henry Nolan Mettetal (November 19, 1945 – December 28, 2020) was an American politician. He was a member of the Republican party. Mettetal was member of the Mississippi House of Representatives from 2012 to 2020. He also was a member of the Mississippi Senate from 1996 to 2012. Mettetal was born in Baton Rouge, Louisiana.
Mettetal died of COVID-19 on December 28, 2020 at a hospital in Oxford, Mississippi at age 75.
